Package: PopCon
Type: Package
Title: Design and Analysis for Population Average Marginal Component Effects
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Naoki Egami, Brandon de la Cuesta, Kosuke Imai
Maintainer: Naoki Egami <naoki.egami5@gmail.com>
Description: Provides design-based and model-based estimators for the population average marginal component effects in general factorial experiments, including conjoint analysis.The package also implements a series of recommendations offered in de la Cuesta, Egami, and Imai(2019).
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
